      "role": "user",
      "content": "i mean \"economic anxieties\" sounds a bit subjective... like is there a real risk of the grid failing or is that just what they want people to think? and honestly shouldn't we just accept that coal is dying anyway? seems like a waste of time to debate it if the transition is inevitable.",
